OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776395018
OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,FEurope has "maybe six weeks or so (of)
OL,7,Fjet fuel left" the head of the
OL,8,FInternational Energy Agency said on
OL,9,FThursday, warning of possible flight
OL,10,Fcancellations "soon" if oil supplies
OL,11,Fremain blocked by the Iran war.
OL,13,FIEA Executive Director Fatih Birol
OL,14,Fsaid that the world is experiencing
OL,15,F"the largest energy crisis we have
OL,16,Fever faced," stemming from the ongoing
OL,17,Fclosure of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,18,Fthrough which a fifth of global oil
OL,19,Ftransits in peacetime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
