FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776395018
OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,F"In the past there was a group called
OL,7,FDire Straits," he said. "It's a dire
OL,8,Fstrait now, and it is going to have
OL,9,Fmajor implications for the global
OL,10,Feconomy.
OL,12,F"And the longer it goes, the worse it
OL,13,Fwill be for the economic growth and
OL,14,Finflation around the world."
OL,16,FThe impact will be "higher petrol
OL,17,F(gasoline) prices, higher gas prices,
OL,18,Fhigh electricity prices," Birol told
OL,19,Fthe Associated Press.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
