OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FEconomic pain will be felt unevenly,
OL,12,Fwith some countries "hit worse than
OL,13,Fthe others," he said, naming Japan,
OL,14,FKorea, India, China, Pakistan and
OL,15,FBangladesh as being on the front line
OL,16,Fof the energy crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
