FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776395018
OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,F"The countries who will suffer the
OL,7,Fmost will not be those whose voices
OL,8,Fare heard a lot. It will be mainly the
OL,9,Fdeveloping countries. Poorer countries
OL,10,Fin Asia, in Africa, and in Latin
OL,11,FAmerica," he said. "Then it will come
OL,12,Fto Europe and the Americas."
OL,14,FIf the Strait of Hormuz isn't
OL,15,Freopened, he said European airlines
OL,16,Fwould be forced to cancel flights.
OL,18,F"I can tell you soon we will hear the
OL,19,Fnews that some of the flights from
OL,20,Fcity A to city B might be cancelled as
OL,21,Fa result of lack of jet fuel," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
