CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776395018
OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,FHis comments come after easyJet warned
OL,7,Fthat the airline is expected to suffer
OL,8,Fa loss of #540 million to #560 million
OL,9,Ffor the six months to the end of
OL,10,FMarch, compared with a #394 million
OL,11,Floss for the same period last year.
OL,13,FThe airline said it remained confident
OL,14,Fin its fuel supplies for the near
OL,15,Ffuture until at least the middle of
OL,16,FMay.
OL,18,FThey also noted bookings are down 2%
OL,19,Ffor the three months to the end of
OL,20,Fboth June and September compared with
OL,21,Fa year ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
