PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776395018
OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,FEuropean airports have also been
OL,7,Fsounding the alarm over fuel
OL,8,Fshortages, with the Airports Council
OL,9,FInternational (ACI), which represents
OL,10,Fmore than 600 airports, last week
OL,11,Fissuing a letter to the EU outlining
OL,12,Fimminent issues.
OL,14,FThe body's director-general Olivier
OL,15,FJankovec wrote in the letter: "At this
OL,16,Fstage, we understand that if the
OL,17,Fpassage through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,18,Fdoes not resume in any significant and
OL,19,Fstable way within the next three
OL,20,Fweeks, systemic jet fuel shortage is
OL,21,Fset to become a reality for the EU.
OL,26,@wD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
