OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776395018
OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,F"The fact that we are entering the
OL,7,Fpeak summer season... is only adding
OL,8,Fto those concerns."
OL,10,FRyanair's boss Michael O'Leary said
OL,11,Fearlier this month that if the war
OL,12,Fcontinues, then there was a risk of
OL,13,F"disruptions in Europe in May and
OL,14,FJune", adding that "maybe 10%, 20%,
OL,15,F25% of our supplies might be at risk".
OL,17,FBirol said more than 110 oil-laden
OL,18,Ftankers are waiting in the Persian
OL,19,FGulf and could help ease the energy
OL,20,Fcrisis if they could escape through
OL,21,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SO]uD@AOUvD@EO]vD@TOUwD@eO]
