OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,F"But it is not enough," he added.
OL,8,FEven with a peace deal, strikes on
OL,9,Fenergy facilities means it could be
OL,10,Fmany months before pre-war production
OL,11,Flevels are restored, he said.
OL,13,F"Over 80 key assets in the region have
OL,14,Fbeen damaged. And out of these 80,
OL,15,Fmore than one third are severely or
OL,16,Fvery severely damaged," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@WO]uD@AOUxD@WO]
