OL,3,CEurope has 'maybe 6 weeks' of jet fuel
OL,4,Cleft, energy agency head warns
OL,6,F"It will be extremely optimistic to
OL,7,Fbelieve that it will very quick,"
OL,8,FBirol said. "It will take gradually,
OL,9,Fgradually, up to two years to come
OL,10,Fback where we were before the war."
